{"tid":2403910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"房門被貼咗兩張保皇黨揮春...","createTime":"2021-02-11T11:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T12:19:12.000Z","uid":345689,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ee6f80ab57ae4e6d781c66511eafdcec00953d93","tid":2403910,"uid":345689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"收爐番到屋企，就見到房門貼咗兩張淫賤聯揮春... 一問之下，係老豆貼上去嘅... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B5neQSn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB5neQSn.jpg&h=d7b77e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後再望下屋企大門入面，貼咗兩張李志宏手寫嘅揮春<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fso9ELN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffso9ELN.jpg&h=535c0ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住就意識到，老豆純粹係見有位就貼揮春 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （不過一直佢都無留意黃藍）<br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過喺木門上搣揮春係唔會整爛張嘢？<br />\n<br />\n老豆係好傳統嘅人嚟，如果搣爛咗又唔老黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036d881d102f375f982f77d94c8e2f7620f0ed92","tid":2403910,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:20:40.000Z","msg":"換咗都唔記得啦下話"},{"pid":"8d582e073bb46592b155ee63cac7b8a1dc6aaa08","tid":2403910,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:21:59.000Z","msg":"我專拎  人地資源點解唔拎<br />\n<br />\n對家咪一樣會拎飯民d資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26859fdf9b485f4a83d192b2410e4802f7f1e3d","tid":2403910,"uid":7125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:22:32.000Z","msg":"貼上貼試下？搵張岩岩大啲啲既"},{"pid":"d18141093cba38142c2e4f2015de70d4c392fdf6","tid":2403910,"uid":159307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:22:48.000Z","msg":"一係搣一係𠝹"},{"pid":"e8bfc685f10977428b36ee1c0521a454e925b9f8","tid":2403910,"uid":345689,"like":0,"disli